flowchart TD
    A[Staff/Owner Login] --> B{Select Module}

    B --> C[Turf Booking]
    B --> D[Swimming]
    B --> E[Food Sales]
    B --> F[Other Items Sales]
    B --> G[Dashboard / Billing]

    %% Turf Module
    C --> C1[Pick Date]
    C1 --> C2[View Slots: Available / Booked / Held]
    C2 --> C3{Slot Available?}
    C3 -- Yes --> C4[Enter Customer Name, Phone, Tier, Advance]
    C4 --> C5[Confirm Booking - Slot Locked]
    C3 -- No --> C6[Choose Another Slot or Date]
    C7[Owner: Manage Slots] --> C7a[Add / Edit / Delete Time Slot]
    C7a --> C7b[Set Price per Tier 14/16/18]
    C7b --> C2

    %% Swimming Module
    D --> D1[Enter Number of People + Hours]
    D1 --> D2[Auto-Calculate Price]
    D2 --> D3[Generate Token / Receipt]
    D3 --> D4[Mark Paid / Unpaid]
    D5[Owner: Set/Edit Per-Person-Per-Hour Price] --> D2

    %% Food Module
    E --> E1[Select Item from Product List]
    E1 --> E2[Enter Quantity]
    E2 --> E3[Auto-Calculate Total]
    E3 --> E4[Add More Items?]
    E4 -- Yes --> E1
    E4 -- No --> E5[Generate Bill]
    E6[Owner: Manage Products] --> E6a[Add / Edit / Remove Item + Price]
    E6a --> E1

    %% Other Items Module
    F --> F1[Select Item from Product List]
    F1 --> F2[Enter Quantity]
    F2 --> F3[Auto-Calculate Total]
    F3 --> F4[Add More Items?]
    F4 -- Yes --> F1
    F4 -- No --> F5[Generate Bill]
    F6[Owner: Manage Products] --> F6a[Add / Edit / Remove Item + Price]
    F6a --> F1

    %% Dashboard
    C5 --> G
    D4 --> G
    E5 --> G
    F5 --> G
    G --> G1[Daily Revenue by Category]
    G --> G2[Monthly Revenue Summary]
    G --> G3[Revenue Charts]
    G --> G4[Printable / Shareable Bill]
